                <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Accessibility Trainings
</h1>
                        <div class="block block-system block-main block-system-main odd block-without-title" id="block-system-main">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
            
    <div class="content clearfix">
      <div class="view view-it-academy-accessibility-trainings view-id-it_academy_accessibility_trainings view-display-id-page_1 view-dom-id-500873a151451992fe27a72f015957be">
            <div class="view-header">
      <h2>IT Academy: On-Demand Accessibility Trainings</h2>
<p>Our team offers online trainings that you can do on your own schedule.  View the trainings by role or find a specific training in the filtered view below.</p>
<p>Select any filter below and click on Apply to see results.</p>
<p>Note: The role of Content Creator is someone who creates or edits digital content or information.  Examples of digital content are web pages, images, videos, audio files, emails, social media posts, and PDFs.</p>
    </div>
  
      <div class="view-filters">
      <form action="/web-accessibility/training" method="get" id="views-exposed-form-it-academy-accessibility-trainings-page-1" accept-charset="UTF-8"><div><div class="views-exposed-form">
